Notice to Members No.  01-312

September 24, 2001


TO:             All NYMEX Division Members

                All NYMEX Commodity Managers

                All NYMEX Clearing Members


FROM:   J. Robert Collins, Jr., President


RE:             Posting of All NYMEX Division EFPs


Posting of all EFPs for all NYMEX Division futures contracts, as required by

NYMEX Division Rule 6.21(B) will be extended until 4:30 P.M. until otherwise

notified.


Any questions can be directed to Thomas LaSala, Vice President, Compliance,

at (212) 299-2897.
